        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Black Lung Benefits Disability Trust Fund Solvency Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill extends until December 31, 2031, the excise tax on coal. The revenues from such tax provide funding for the Black Lung Disability Trust Fund.</p>]]>
        </text>
